<br>
I always have the most trouble keeping Rangers alive, with both low HP and low AF. In a group of three Rangers and a Druid, I expect more deaths for you and yours than normal.<br>
<br>
If you can convince one of them to be a Hero (first) then another to be an Eldritch (second), you'd have a fairly balanced group (just need a Bard now).<br>
